---
title: Caramelised Pear & Pecan Pancakes with Syrup & Cream | Serves 2
description: Decadent and fluffy, these pancakes are a weekend brunch must. Plus they're topped with the works: caramelised pear and nuts, cream and drizzled with maple-flavoured syrup. Pile them high, pair with your favourite drink and indulge!
